---

<Layout
  title="AI-Рендер — фотореалистичная визуализация фасадов"
  description="Фотореалистичная визуализация фасадов за секунды. AI-рендеринг в 4K качестве. 10 архитектурных стилей. От 990 ₽ за 5 рендеров."
  keywords="AI рендер, визуализация фасада, рендер дома, 3D визуализация экстерьера, фотореалистичный рендер"
  ogImage="/images/og-render.jpg"
  canonical="/render"
  transparentHeader={true}
>
  <main>
    <!-- СЕКЦИЯ 1: Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A4C76] via-[#1A7BB3] to-[#92CF93] overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Blur decorations -->
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-[#92CF93]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-[#1A7BB3]/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-32 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-medium rounded-full text-sm mb-6 border border-white/20">
            AI-Рендер
          </span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
            Фотореалистичный фасад<br />за 30 секунд
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Превратите 3D модель или планировку в фотореалистичную визуализацию экстерьера.
            AI создаст качественные рендеры фасада за считанные секунды — выберите стиль, ракурс и время суток.
          </p>

          <!-- Feature Pills -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-sm rounded-full">10-30 секунд</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-sm rounded-full">4K качество</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-sm rounded-full">10 стилей</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-sm rounded-full">990 ₽ / 5 рендеров</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="https://studio.planometrica.ru/render"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0A4C76] bg-white rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg"
            >
              Создать рендер
              <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#styles"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/30 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
            >
              Смотреть стили
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/60" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- СЕКЦИЯ 2: Возможности (6 карточек) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#92CF93]/20 text-[#1A7BB3] font-medium rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
            Возможности
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Визуализация нового поколения
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            AI-рендеринг вместо часов ожидания в традиционных программах
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {capabilities.map((item) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0A4C76]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A4C76] mb-4">
                <Fragment set:html={item.icon} />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">{item.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- СЕКЦИЯ 3: Галерея стилей (10 стилей) -->
    <section id="styles" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#0A4C76]/10 text-[#0A4C76] font-medium rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
            10 архитектурных стилей
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Выберите стиль фасада
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Библиотека готовых стилей для экстерьера вашего дома
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {styles.map((style) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#0A4C76] hover:shadow-lg transition-all cursor-pointer group">
              <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:from-[#0A4C76]/5 group-hover:to-[#1A7BB3]/5 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#0A4C76] transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 002.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">{style.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">{style.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- СЕКЦИЯ 4: Цена и сравнение -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#92CF93]/20 text-[#1A7BB3] font-medium rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
            Цены
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            AI-Рендер vs Традиционный рендеринг
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Price Card -->
        <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A4C76] to-[#1A7BB3] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">990 ₽</div>
            <div class="text-white/80 mb-6">за 5 рендеров экстерьера</div>
            <ul class="text-left space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                5 фотореалистичных рендеров
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Любой из 10 стилей
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Разные ракурсы и время суток
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Экспорт в 4K качестве
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">
              Включено в Стандарт-пакет (14 900 ₽)
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://studio.planometrica.ru/render"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3 text-[#0A4C76] bg-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Создать рендер
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Comparison -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center mb-12">
            <div>
              <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#0A4C76] mb-2">30 сек</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">AI-Рендер</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-300 mb-2">vs</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2">4+ ч</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">Традиционный рендер</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#92CF93] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  AI-Рендер
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    Результат за секунды
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    Не требует мощного ПК
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    Автоматическая настройка света
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#92CF93]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                    10 готовых стилей фасадов
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  Традиционный
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                    Часы ожидания рендера
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                    Нужна видеокарта от $1000
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                    Ручная настройка освещения
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                    Нужны текстуры и материалы
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- СЕКЦИЯ 5: CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A4C76] via-[#1A7BB3] to-[#0A4C76] relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Blur decorations -->
      <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Создайте первый рендер бесплатно
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
            Загрузите модель или планировку — получите фотореалистичную визуализацию фасада за секунды.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="https://studio.planometrica.ru/render"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold bg-[#92CF93] text-[#0A4C76] rounded-xl hover:bg-[#7ec07f] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            >
              Создать рендер
